	Photon Race

4k procedural graphics compo contribution  for Buenzli 2008, Switzerland


Features
 - Raytracing
 - Photontracing
 - Caustics
 - Constructive Solide Geometry (3d boolean)
 - depth of field
 - flare effect

Takes about 20sec to compile shaders, then all done in the GPU. 
Finished on the party one minute before the deadline


